Al Hunt, executive editor at 
Bloomberg News, talks about Texas Governor Rick Perry's entry 
into the Republican presidential race.  Hunt, speaking on Bloomberg Television's "InBusiness With 
Margaret Brennan," also discusses President Barack Obama's 
three-day bus tour through the Midwest. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 03:25
 